==In the media== Ganor has been covered in leading publications such as Der Spiegel,<ref>{{cite news |last=Kerbusk |first=Klaus_Peter |year=2001 |title=Attack Von Bill Gates |newspaper=''Der Spiegel'' |location= Germany}}</ref> Die Zeit,<ref>{{cite news|date=August 16, 1996 |title=Telefonieren übers Internet wird salonfähig |newspaper=''Die Zeit'' |location= Germany}}</ref> Wall Street Journal,<ref name ="wallstreetjournal">{{cite journal | last = Bulkeley | first = William M. | date = February 10, 1995 | title = Hello World! Audible chats On the Internet | journal = Wall Street Journal}}</ref> BusinessWeek,<ref>{{cite journal | last = Tanaka | first = Jamie | date = October 27, 1997 | title =You're Coming Over Loud and Almost Clear | journal = BusinessWeek}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal | last = Mermelstein | first = Jeff | date = April 22, 1996 | title =Try Beating These Long-Distance Rates | journal = BusinessWeek}}</ref> Newsweek,<ref>{{cite journal | last = Levy | first = Steven | date = May 13, 1996 | title = Calling All Computers | journal = Newsweek}}</ref> Von Magazine,<ref name="von">{{cite journal | last = Pulver | first = Jeff | date = September 2003 |title = Elon Ganor of VocalTec | journal = Von Magazine}}</ref> Computer Business,<ref> {{cite journal | last = Lawrence | first = Andrew | date = January 1998 | journal = Computer Business}}</ref> WebWeek,<ref> {{cite journal | last = Hertzberg | first = Robert | date = December 1, 1997 |title = Internet Telephony's Pioneer | journal = WebWeek}}</ref> Industry Standard,<ref>{{cite journal |last=Krause |first=Jason |date=December 27, 1999 |title=The Return of Elon Ganor |journal=The Industry Standard}}</ref> and Time magazine.<ref>{{cite magazine |last= Quittner |first= Joshua |date=March 27, 1995 |title=Talk Gets Very Cheap |magazine=Time Magazine}}</ref> He has appeared many times on most main television networks such as CNN,<ref name="cnn">{{cite news| last= Clancy| first = Jim| date = October 10, 1995| title= Internet phone makes global chatting cheaper| url = http://edition.cnn.com/TECH/9510/internet_phone/index.html| website = http://edition.cnn.com/}}</ref> and participated as a panelist many times at the prestigious [[World Economic Forum]] in Davos, Switzerland.<ref name="von" />
